props.text:
The Path is the how you earn and provide value.

What careers, industries, and business opportunities you can work on.

It is where and how you spend your attention.

The Craft is your practice, your effort.

Your skills, knowledge, expertise, and strengths.

It is how you shape the world.

The Heart is the core of who you are.

Your interests, values, influences, and dreams. 

The Heart is your guide.

The Cause is what you care about 
and what problems the world needs solving.

Welcome to Journey, 
an app inspired by the Japanese concept of IKIGAI.
In Journey, you will explore 4 areas of your being.
